<br>
A warrior replaced me in a Fire Castle group the other day...  the party didn't seem to slow down at all.  The number of kills/time was around the same in my parse as before as well.  (He replaced a paladin, and I switched to damage dealing -well trying hehe)  Note, to be fair, we were clearing the castle... and continued to at about the same rate...<br>
<br>
Was I better at hate generation?  Yes, but not noticeably...  similar to the mitigation difference between knights and Warriors.<br>
<br>
That one drop (BoW) closed the gap for hate generation for that warrior quite nicely.<br>
