Yes, Knights and rangers can use the BoW, but the weapon benefits a Warrior more than any other class.  Rangers view the proc as a curse...  Knights will gain in hate generation efficiency, but not gain anywhere near as much as warriors, as their spells do that...  and indeed the knights do not gain as much from the weapon's damage as the warriors do either.<br>
